com.didisoft.pgp
Interface HashAlgorithm

public interface HashAlgorithm

Interface that lists the supported hashing algorithms used in the library.

Example usage

 PGPLib pgp = new PGPLib();
 pgp.setHash(HashAlgorithm.SHA256);

Since:
2.5
